reviewText: This is a great movie.  I was so happy to see a new holiday movie from The Wiggles, so I snapped it up on prebook.  It has since arrived, and we've been watching it even though we're still weeks away from the holidays. This DVD has been a huge hit in our house!  There are tons of songs, from the familiar to brand-new, and lots of opportunity to get up and dance. Very interactive. The Dorothy animated bonus movie is really cute, too.  The DVD is almost 2 hours long for under $10-- pretty awesome.  Highly recommended.
summary: Fantastic new movie from The Wiggles!
Title: The Wiggles: It's Always Christmas With You!

reviewText: We absolutely love this DVD!  It is great. Sam Moran and the Wiggles are great.  My 20 month old dances and enjoys every song. Our favorite is Joey Fatone and O Holy Night.  Anuna is awesome too.  We watch this DVD over and over and over ..This DVD is the BEST OF THE WIGGLES!!14 Songs included:It's Always Christmas With You!The Cherry Tree Carol (Featuring Anún(Irish choral group))O Holy Night (Featuring Joey Fatone of N'SYNC)It's a Long Way From the North PoleDing Dong Merrily on High (Featuring Anúna)A Miracle in a Manger (Featuring John Paul Young)Jingle Bell RockWe Three Kings (Featuring Anúna)The Turkey Jumps Right Out of the PieThe Twelve Days of ChristmasI Just Can't Sleep on Christmas Eve!The Little Drummer Boy (Featuring Anúna)Bobby Wants a Puppy Dog for ChristmasWill You Dance With Me Around the Christmas Tree
summary: AWESOME!! LOVE THIS DVD!! MISS SAM MORAN
Title: The Wiggles: It's Always Christmas With You!

reviewText: We have seen all the wiggle Xmas except for this one. Santa got it n they enjoy it. Like also the Dorothy animation on the special features.
Title: The Wiggles: It's Always Christmas With You!

reviewText: Cute video, great scenery, and wonderful Christmas songs. I'm a grandmother, and I enjoyed them along with my granddaughter. Some of the songs are very catchy and will revisit your memory at times. The video is also about the true meaning of Christmas...and as such, I was truly grateful.
summary: The Wiggles: It's Always Christmas With You!
Title: The Wiggles: It's Always Christmas With You!

reviewText: My grandson loves the Wiggles and this was a great Birthday present prior to Christmas. Plays it everyday. Would recommend all Wiggles DVD's they are great
